hism, or onto the climate contrast between the snowy Himalaya and the warm Terai."}]]}],["$","article","As long as sky bodies shine",{"className":"flex h-full min-h-0 flex-col rounded-sm border p-6 md:p-7 border-charcoal/12 bg-charcoal/[0.04]","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.26em] text-charcoal/45","children":"Perpetuity"}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"mt-2 font-display text-xl font-bold text-charcoal","children":"As long as sky bodies shine"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 flex-1 text-[13px] leading-[1.85] text-charcoal/[0.55]","children":"Including both luminaries telegraphs the hope that Nepal lasts as long as celestial lights — a poetic line often repeated in reference works alongside the drier legal description of twelve solar rays and sixteen lunar rays (eight visible)."}]]}]]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mt-16 rounded-sm bg-charcoal px-6 py-9 text-cream md:mt-20 md:px-10 md:py-11","aria-labelledby":"geometry-heading","children":[["$","p",null,{"lang":"ne","className":"text-gold/75 font-nepali text-[14px] font-medium leading-relaxed tracking-[0em] normal-case antialiased md:text-[16px] [text-rendering:optimizeLegibility]","children":"ज्यामिति र अन्तर्राष्ट्रिय प्रयोग"}],["$","h2",null,{"id":"geometry-heading","className":"mt-2 font-display text-2xl font-bold md:text-3xl","children":"Where the math surprises visitors"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3 md:items-stretch","children":[["$","article","Irrational outer ratio",{"className":"flex h-full min-h-0 flex-col rounded-sm border border-cream/12 bg-cream/[0.04] p-5 md:p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-display text-lg text-gold","children":"Irrational outer ratio"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 flex-1 text-[13px] leading-[1.85] text-cream/50","children":"When you follow Nepal’s geometric construction verbatim, height : maximum width settles at an irrational value ≈ 1 : 1.21901033… catalogued as 